# Blog Configuration
# ==================

# Client-side blog URL (used in browser for links)
# Production: Uses /blog (nginx proxy) - this is the DEFAULT, no need to set
# Local development: Uncomment and use external URL in your .env.local
# NEXT_PUBLIC_BLOG_URL=https://redem.c3sl.ufpr.br/blog

# Server-side WordPress API URL (used for fetch calls in Node.js)
# Production: Uses http://127.0.0.1:8081 by default (direct localhost)
# Local development: Set to external URL in your .env.local
# BLOG_API_URL=https://redem.c3sl.ufpr.br/blog
